::Zardus/Reptilica::

Zardus turns to look at Dark One, many thoughts rushing through his head. He 
wasn't sure that they had enough energon to pay the mercenaries. That wasn't 
good. Zardus looks at Dark One for a moment, his eyes neutral, not giving off 
any hint of what he was thinking.

"Oh, yeah," Reptilica said from behind Zardus, "Me and Bloodystrike mined ya 
some energon while you were off having your battle fun. It's all in the cargo 
hold."

Zardus lets out a silent breath of relief, getting up.

"Your energon is ready," he says, "Would you like to take it right now?"
